Tk-StatusBar version 0.03
=========================

Tk-Statusbar is a composit Tk widget derived from a Tk-Frame.  The
statusbar can be split up into any number of sections.  A section
can contain either a label or a progress bar.  Each section can
also be configured with a fixed width or a variable width.  Events
can be bound to sections providing interactivity with the statusbar.
The statusbar can also be hidden restored.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or

   Just put the StatusBar.pm file somewhere where Perl can find it.
   The StatusBar is written in pure perl.


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Tk


